{
    "poem_title": "Juif",
    "author": "Germain Nouveau",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1922",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Quelqu’un qui jamais ne se trompe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "M’appelle juif… Moi, juif ? Pourquoi ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Je suis chrétien, sans que je rompe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Le pain bénit à son de trompe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Bien qu’en mon trou… je reste coi.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quelqu’un qui jamais ne se trompe,\nM’appelle juif… Moi, juif ? Pourquoi ?\nJe suis chrétien, sans que je rompe\nLe pain bénit à son de trompe,\nBien qu’en mon trou… je reste coi."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Je sais juif, ah ! c’est bien possible !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Je n’ai le nez spirituel",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Ni l’air résigné d’une cible ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Je ne montre un cœur insensible.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Tout juif est-il en Israël ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je sais juif, ah ! c’est bien possible !\nJe n’ai le nez spirituel\nNi l’air résigné d’une cible ;\nJe ne montre un cœur insensible.\nTout juif est-il en Israël ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Mais si juif signifie avare",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Économisant sur le suif,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Sur l’eau qui pourtant n’est pas rare",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Sur une corde de guitare,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Je me fais honneur d’être juif.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais si juif signifie avare\nÉconomisant sur le suif,\nSur l’eau qui pourtant n’est pas rare\nSur une corde de guitare,\nJe me fais honneur d’être juif."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Je prends pour moi seul cette injure,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Quoique je ne possède rien ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Je me l’écris sur la figure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "En trois mots, sans une rature ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Voyez : je suis juif. Lisez bien.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je prends pour moi seul cette injure,\nQuoique je ne possède rien ;\nJe me l’écris sur la figure\nEn trois mots, sans une rature ;\nVoyez : je suis juif. Lisez bien."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Regardez-moi : ma barbe est sale",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Comme en chaire un prédicateur",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Qui vide une fosse nasale,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Et j’ai l’aspect froid d’une stalle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Dans le temple où prêche un pasteur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Regardez-moi : ma barbe est sale\nComme en chaire un prédicateur\nQui vide une fosse nasale,\nEt j’ai l’aspect froid d’une stalle,\nDans le temple où prêche un pasteur."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Moi, juif, je mens, je calomnie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Comme un misérable chrétien,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Lorsqu’à tort il affirme ou nie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Ou qu’il dispute, ô vilenie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "En parlant du mien et du tien ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Moi, juif, je mens, je calomnie,\nComme un misérable chrétien,\nLorsqu’à tort il affirme ou nie,\nOu qu’il dispute, ô vilenie !\nEn parlant du mien et du tien ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "J’adore un veau d’or… dans ma bague,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Le veau qu’on débite en bijoux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Au seul mot d’argent, je divague,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Comme le catholique vague",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Qui ne se passe de joujoux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’adore un veau d’or… dans ma bague,\nLe veau qu’on débite en bijoux ;\nAu seul mot d’argent, je divague,\nComme le catholique vague\nQui ne se passe de joujoux ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Moi, fils de ceux qui portaient l’Arche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Je ris, et je laisse périr,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Je perds la foi du patriarche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Comme tout un peuple qui marche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Vers l’ombre où le corps doit pourrir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Moi, fils de ceux qui portaient l’Arche,\nJe ris, et je laisse périr,\nJe perds la foi du patriarche,\nComme tout un peuple qui marche\nVers l’ombre où le corps doit pourrir."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Moi, juif, je doute de mon âme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Moi, juif, je doute de l’Amour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Je ne suis sûr que de ma femme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "(N’est-ce pas étrange, Madame ?)",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Comme bien des… maris du jour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Moi, juif, je doute de mon âme,\nMoi, juif, je doute de l’Amour,\nJe ne suis sûr que de ma femme,\n(N’est-ce pas étrange, Madame ?)\nComme bien des… maris du jour."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Car elle se fout de la vogue",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Qu’a tout argument inventé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Par notre science un peu rogue ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Elle aime mieux la synagogue",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Si fraîche, dès l’aube, en été.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car elle se fout de la vogue\nQu’a tout argument inventé\nPar notre science un peu rogue ;\nElle aime mieux la synagogue\nSi fraîche, dès l’aube, en été."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Elle est blanche, elle a sur les tempes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Une perruque où rit sa fleur ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Faite à souhait pour les estampes ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Quand elle adore sous les lampes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Dans ses voiles d’une couleur ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elle est blanche, elle a sur les tempes\nUne perruque où rit sa fleur ;\nFaite à souhait pour les estampes ;\nQuand elle adore sous les lampes\nDans ses voiles d’une couleur ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Elle se consume en prières,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Conservant, sans en rien verser,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "L’eau de ses croyances entières,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Car… une douzaine de pierres",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Ça suffit pour recommencer.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elle se consume en prières,\nConservant, sans en rien verser,\nL’eau de ses croyances entières,\nCar… une douzaine de pierres\nÇa suffit pour recommencer."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Jérusalem les garde encore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Salomon les reçut du Ciel",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Qu’avec des larmes elle implore ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Comme une juive que j’adore,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "L’épouse de Nathaniel.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Jérusalem les garde encore,\nSalomon les reçut du Ciel\nQu’avec des larmes elle implore ;\nComme une juive que j’adore,\nL’épouse de Nathaniel."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Ce qu’on admire fort sur elle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "C’est l’honneur de faire de l’art",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Par une pente naturelle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Pas pour vendre son aquarelle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Ni pour manger un peu de lard.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ce qu’on admire fort sur elle,\nC’est l’honneur de faire de l’art\nPar une pente naturelle,\nPas pour vendre son aquarelle,\nNi pour manger un peu de lard."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "J’ai pu contempler sa peinture,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Dans une salle au Luxembourg :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "C’est très bien peint d’après nature ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "C’est avec l’eau, sous la toiture,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Ça me semble, un coin de faubourg.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’ai pu contempler sa peinture,\nDans une salle au Luxembourg :\nC’est très bien peint d’après nature ;\nC’est avec l’eau, sous la toiture,\nÇa me semble, un coin de faubourg."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 16,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Sur la cimaise elle est sous verre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Je puis donc y mettre un baiser",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Loin des yeux du gardien sévère ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Bref, l’art charmant qu’elle sait faire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "C’est, comme il sied, pour s’amuser.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sur la cimaise elle est sous verre,\nJe puis donc y mettre un baiser\nLoin des yeux du gardien sévère ;\nBref, l’art charmant qu’elle sait faire,\nC’est, comme il sied, pour s’amuser."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 17,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Cela ne fait l’ombre d’un doute",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "Pour tous, dans la société ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Oui, ma belle Mignonne, écoute,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "Elle pourrait épater toute",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "La pâle catholicité.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Cela ne fait l’ombre d’un doute\nPour tous, dans la société ;\nOui, ma belle Mignonne, écoute,\nElle pourrait épater toute\nLa pâle catholicité."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 18,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
                    "line_text": "Tiens ! En veux-tu rien qu’un exemple ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
